verbose_text: In the Y79 retinoblastoma cell line, the mRNA levels of cdc25A, CDK2 and p21 were significantly lower in the PAX6 inhibition study group than in negative GFP-control group (cdc25A, 0.36 +/-0.07 vs. 1.00 +/-0.00; t = 15.91; P < 0.01, n = 3; CDK2, 0.28 +/-0.03 vs. 1.00 +/-0.00; t = 46.77; P < 0.01, n = 3; p21, 0.37 +/-0.08 vs. 1.00 +/-0.00; t = 14.37; P < 0.01, n = 3) (XREF_FIG).
